WEBVTT

00:04:00.680 --> 00:04:01.976
AG: No. At five?

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.176
(Laughter)

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:04.760
AH: At five, yes.

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:08.656
I mean, I'm sure I was reading
probably coloring books

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:10.296
but whatever it was,

00:04:10.320 --> 00:04:14.496
I felt this was more important
than socializing at that moment.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:19.016
Nancy Rothbard: What we find is that those
kind of unhappy workaholics we think of,

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:22.280
people who are obsessed with their jobs
but actually don't love them,

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:26.056
those folks really are at higher risk.

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.496
AG: That's my colleague Nancy Rothbard,

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:31.949
a leading expert on how people manage
the boundary between work and life.